Stay in the heart of Athens – Excellent location – show map

One of our best sellers in Athens! Located within walking distance of major touristic attractions and vibrant areas of the city, Athens Backpackers are just a stone's throw from the world-renowned Acropolis of Athens. It has a seasonal rooftop bar with views over the Acropolis, and offers free WiFi access throughout.

Athens Backpackers features air-conditioned rooms. All include shared bathrooms, some of which are en suite, and most open to a balcony. Bed linen is provided.

You will find a 24-hour front desk at the property. The rooftop bar creates an ideal setting for social nights during the summer months, while guests may also relax at the shared courtyard. Shared facilities also include an industrial-style, well-equipped kitchen.

The central location of Athens Backpackers favors direct access to a range of night clubs, bars and traditional taverns. History lovers will be thrilled to find out that Acropolis and its museum is at just 500 feet. The vibrant Monastiraki, boasting an array of dining and shopping options, is located within approximately 0.9 mi of Athens Backpackers. Athens International Airport is at 24 mi.

This is our guests' favorite part of Athens, according to independent reviews.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 9.7 for a two-person trip.
